# ACTIONS
#-------------------------------------------------------------------#
$AQUERY_ACTION
Local Char CURPRO(250),CURPTH(250),AMETHOD(50),AEVENT(50)
[L]AEVENT = [L]ACTION
Gosub METHODS From SIVINVINQM_RSTD
Gosub EVENTS From SIVINVINQM_RSTD
Return
 


